All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    addOns
    The addOns class extends the Page class as a specific page in the GUI which host all the modifications for a drink
    cart
    JPanel extention class that controls a active cart used as a side bar in the GUI
    category
    Category extends the page class and acts as a subset of the window that displays the category options in the GUI
    CustomTableModel
    Extension of default table model that enables editability of specific cells and rows.
    DbFunctions  
    Drink
    Drink class that is used to represent a Drink row in the system, which can be constructed based on query pull or user for pushing back to the database
    drinkPage
    drinkPage extends the page class and acts as a subset of the window that displays the drink options under the selected category in the GUI
    GUIMain
    The main class to execute to generate the GUI
    header
    Header extends the JPanel class as a permenant panel on the GUI.
    inventory
    Inventory extends the page and allows the user the edit the inventory table in the database: add, remove, and edit items, their prices, names and stock levels.
    Item
    Drink class that is used to represent a Drink row in the system, which can be constructed based on query pull or user for pushing back to the database
    login
    Login extends the page class and creates a login page for the GUI so that users can login to the system
    manageItems
    manageItems extends the page class and acts as a page that allows the user to add, remove, and edit items on the menu in the GUI.
    manageUsers
    Creates card for Manage Users functions and data display.
    Order
    Order class used to reflect the members of an order in the system, can be used for push and pull to database
    orderTrends
    Creates card for Order Trend functions and data display.
    Page
    Base class for all card panels.
    signUp
    Creates card for Sign Up functionality.
    window
    Constructs JFrame that contains all cards and JPanels as well as the information associated with them
